/>\n唯一一條線<br />\n獨市行某幾個站（三聖  建安  山景南  山景北）<br />\n但等車時間冠絕全線輕鐵<br />\n負責規劃果條撚樣係咪腦裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇咩建議可以討論吓"},{"pid":"b647b59f0d514c0c6c2d0dc6700585ad08a75c31","tid":464933,"uid":148485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:11:12.000Z","msg":"614,614p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連住嚟連住走，一走又等10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n論多人705,706都唔輸蝕，又係滿瀉"},{"pid":"9b08f18ffcfab0b3d25ff21122312332cb670768","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>505最撚on9 既地方係<br />\n唯一一條線<br />\n獨市行某幾個站（三聖  建安  山景南  山景北）<br />\n但等車時間冠絕全線輕鐵<br />\n負責規劃果條撚樣係咪腦裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇咩建議可以討論吓</blockquote><br />\n610 614 615 3條都係屯碼去元朗<br />\n其實610同615可以兜入山景幫輕下"},{"pid":"4e8aece44ee25531e9e05dd9b420df3df3e40cc6","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>614,614p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連住嚟連住走，一走又等10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n論多人705,706都唔輸蝕，又係滿瀉</blockquote><br />\n個到站時間根本係一個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08dbcca9ab1867aee2ff34b853e0761cf70aa1e9","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>614,614p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連住嚟連住走，一走又等10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n論多人705,706都唔輸蝕，又係滿瀉</blockquote><br />\n個到站時間根本係一個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n614同614p"},{"pid":"88bafb1c0fd99a8f5d6f4511f2eccf8114ebd716","tid":464933,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>505最撚on9 既地方係<br />\n唯一一條線<br />\n獨市行某幾個站（三聖  建安  山景南  山景北）<br />\n但等車時間冠絕全線輕鐵<br />\n負責規劃果條撚樣係咪腦裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇咩建議可以討論吓</blockquote><br />\n講聲唔好意思先  我無認真研究過<br />\n但留意到505個等候時間實在係難以接受<br />\n再者三聖都算係一個孤島<br />\n但人口其實唔少而且極依賴輕鐵做接駁<br />\n<br />\n雖然三聖站有61m/k51/綠van出返市中心<br />\n但佢地班次都係唔夠密  <br />\n仲有3架車既走線都幾遠  <br />\n（實例：<br />\n上以上3架車以西鐵站/屯市做終點目標<br />\n一班比佢地3架車遲8分鐘出發既505係會追返佢地）<br />\n同埋早上繁忙  k51例牌爆車<br />\n<br />\n種種因素都令啲人揀返505  做首選<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n惡性循環黎<br />\n輕鐵應該諗下將505加密班次變雙卡先岩<br />\n<br />\n或者應該咁講 屯門人口太多  <br />\n以前規劃落黎既交通plan已經係解決唔到依家成個屯門既需要（屯公/區內交通）"},{"pid":"10292098432e23442c1acc6e1ba40b1689244c44","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>505最撚on9 既地方係<br />\n唯一一條線<br />\n獨市行某幾個站（三聖  建安  山景南  山景北）<br />\n但等車時間冠絕全線輕鐵<br />\n負責規劃果條撚樣係咪腦裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇咩建議可以討論吓</blockquote><br />\n講聲唔好意思先  我無認真研究過<br />\n但留意到505個等候時間實在係難以接受<br />\n再者三聖都算係一個孤島<br />\n但人口其實唔少而且極依賴輕鐵做接駁<br />\n<br />\n雖然三聖站有61m/k51/綠van出返市中心<br />\n但佢地班次都係唔夠密  <br />\n仲有3架車既走線都幾遠  <br />\n（實例：<br />\n上以上3架車以西鐵站/屯市做終點目標<br />\n一班比佢地3架車遲8分鐘出發既505係會追返佢地）<br />\n同埋早上繁忙  k51例牌爆車<br />\n<br />\n種種因素都令啲人揀返505  做首選<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n惡性循環黎<br />\n輕鐵應該諗下將505加密班次變雙卡先岩<br />\n<br />\n或者應該咁講 屯門人口太多  <br />\n以前規劃落黎既交通plan已經係解決唔到依家成個屯門既需要（屯公/區內交通）</blockquote><br />\n同意 雖然屯門區內係輕鐵專區 未必可以輕易比巴士/小巴區內行走<br />\n但政府或者港鐵應該考慮加密接駁巴士班次 紓緩依家個情況"},{"pid":"f2505750fb5e69a1c7a99e7eb7cbbb203813d0af","tid":464933,"uid":34874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>繁忙時間一定單卡<br />\n少人搭嘅時間就2卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最on9就係你呢d<br />\n繁忙時間孖卡埋唔到站又盛<br />\n非繁忙時間8分鐘一架黎架孖卡好合理</blockquote><br />\n你有冇繁忙時間搭過<br />\n單卡上都上唔到，點清客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係冇咁多車</blockquote><br />\n所以好應該路線重組<br />\nE.g. 615好大程度上同西鐵重複</blockquote><br />\n點重組</blockquote><br />\n615 614可以cut短行車範圍<br />\n以西鐵為重點 輕鐵為接駁</blockquote><br />\n港鐵最近建議過取消614 615 但係505 507同時減一架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/203923_4d7d4e8c4707b0fa13e8922787caef9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F203923_4d7d4e8c4707b0fa13e8922787caef9e.png&h=88b407e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tm/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_doc/ttc/11832/ttc_2017_039.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Ftm%2Fdoc%2F2016_2019%2Ftc%2Fcommittee_meetings_doc%2Fttc%2F11832%2Fttc_2017_039.pdf&d=rn6nqviaFVW1ElLVK9xn%2FgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=eb641c1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tm/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_doc/ttc/11832/ttc_2017_039.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"f3b67b23f5a79c2df0a9472a6e0006d23eaa6566","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T03:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n最on9就係你呢d<br />\n繁忙時間孖卡埋唔到站又盛<br />\n非繁忙時間8分鐘一架黎架孖卡好合理</blockquote><br />\n你有冇繁忙時間搭過<br />\n單卡上都上唔到，點清客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係冇咁多車</blockquote><br />\n所以好應該路線重組<br />\nE.g. 615好大程度上同西鐵重複</blockquote><br />\n點重組</blockquote><br />\n615 614可以cut短行車範圍<br />\n以西鐵為重點 輕鐵為接駁</blockquote><br />\n港鐵最近建議過取消614 615 但係505 507同時減一架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/203923_4d7d4e8c4707b0fa13e8922787caef9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F203923_4d7d4e8c4707b0fa13e8922787caef9e.png&h=88b407e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tm/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_doc/ttc/11832/ttc_2017_039.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Ftm%2Fdoc%2F2016_2019%2Ftc%2Fcommittee_meetings_doc%2Fttc%2F11832%2Fttc_2017_039.pdf&d=rn6nqviaFVW1ElLVK9xn%2FgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=eb641c1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tm/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_doc/ttc/11832/ttc_2017_039.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n505同507都減<br />\n到底佢地有冇搭過下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506326ddf623d6202637a4524986e643829b608b","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"搭緊505<br />\n呢個時間先出孖卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a7b4344ac6c812b1a5d694248ca9318f215ba9","tid":464933,"uid":34874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭緊505<br />\n呢個時間先出孖卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天水圍假日用少咗車 咪施捨幾架比屯門囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629e48605f6025062c8e7a83b0af0c183a8a4467","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭緊505<br />\n呢個時間先出孖卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天水圍假日用少咗