" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F203923_4d7d4e8c4707b0fa13e8922787caef9e.png&h=88b407e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重組完去屯門站仲少咗車 去元朗又唔方便 你真係住屯門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實輕鐵路線唔一定要咁長<br />\n如果跨區 e.g. 屯門去天水圍 / 屯門去元朗<br />\n可以以西鐵為樞紐 輕鐵為駁腳<br />\n輕鐵行車時間短左 或者可以增加班次/拖卡"},{"pid":"5f569b3474d1ea00f0a6bf0d71948fb5e876a195","tid":464933,"uid":34874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早就應該路線重組<br />\n但cut/改任何一條線都會遇到區議會極大阻力 先搞到咁耐以嚟冇次成到事<br />\n大家唔想改搭車習慣 但又日撚日叫輕鐡加車 真係痴閪線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申屯門撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/203923_4d7d4e8c4707b0fa13e8922787caef9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F203923_4d7d4e8c4707b0fa13e8922787caef9e.png&h=88b407e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重組完去屯門站仲少咗車 去元朗又唔方便 你真係住屯門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實輕鐵路線唔一定要咁長<br />\n如果跨區 e.g. 屯門去天水圍 / 屯門去元朗<br />\n可以以西鐵為樞紐 輕鐵為駁腳<br />\n輕鐵行車時間短左 或者可以增加班次/拖卡</blockquote><br />\n長途線少咗兩條 但係505 507反而減車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 自從有一次係大馬路搭761P轉西鐵返屯門 係元朗站見到614出緊嚟 跟住搭507係市中心見返同一架614 之後除非送車尾 如過唔係都廢事轉嚟轉去"},{"pid":"847ec520dac569c7ba56e21872c9c9ab12078135","tid":464933,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"依家坐緊 屯西上迫撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到山景即刻鬆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8244382d32327b334277a0b783dab83044abb0b","tid":464933,"uid":27970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"505都叫迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你搭過610未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb9351681c9f945e3a4460ff1449cd24ad084e9","tid":464933,"uid":140303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"冇左614 615 610 變相西鐵又係會迫爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1d1bc757542f147225ac197dc0a355ca9b3389","tid":464933,"uid":140303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:33:40.000Z","msg":"係山景站冇乜人上615 615p 610 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23869474e3c2270978fd2d3088c2e8097d3e04e6","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>505都叫迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你搭過610未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n610會上唔到車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7915a6a463761969737aec0390d087f7027687","tid":464933,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係山景站冇乜人上615 615p 610 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求其一架兜入建安 經市中心剷返去屯碼都好啦"},{"pid":"439eee930f67f0e3aaee3e147c84378819151e6e","tid":464933,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係山景站冇乜人上615 615p 610 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多係鳴琴落<br />\n除非返學時間有一堆要去求敢揪返學<br />\n610逼應該都係大興果邊<br />\n但去到非繁忙時間都可以塞到滿晒既<br />\n只係見過505係咁<br />\n<br />\n以而家個需求<br />\n好心唔加班次都將啲班次改雙卡啦"},{"pid":"be8482d44be40f199ecf710886030ec544973314","tid":464933,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"有時返到屯門站<br />\n行落去樓下轉巴士舒服過坐505<br />\n起碼都有位坐先<br />\nbtw就快到屯門站 又